    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Check out this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience you can count on. It\u2019s a clean, solid car that\u2019s ready for its next adventure with just the right balance of quality and value. Come see for yourself how great this ride looks and feels!",
